<br>
I recall once when I was in my mid 30s, the typical shouting match between the usual quick-tongued newbie Fier'dal and the often distant and more powerful Tier'dal was taking place. <br>
<br>
The Tier'dal SK, who I will not name due to the fact I can't remember the exact spelling and I know he is still around, was of course threatening the invasion and slaughter of all the innocent women and children of Kelethin blah blah blah. <br>
<br>
Here I was, bearing witness to the numerous newb Fier'dal children shouting back, showing no fear yet not going to meet and rid Greater Faydark of this evil knight, in typical fashion. Well, I did a /who all Dr*******, and saw he was 9 or 10 seasons my superior and without a hitch in my get-a-long, I shouted I would rid Greater Faydark of this tumor that was plaguing our lands. <br>
<br>
By now it was a zone-wide event lol. I ran to the spires where the SK awaited. He obviously immediately conned me and saw I was green to him, and let me I had just chosen my place of buriel. Well, I stood my ground and accepted his duel. As our swords began swinging, it was clear that my life would soon end, as my life was ending faster at a 10:1 ratio compared to his. <br>
<br>
But then, familair sounds began filling my ears. A blessing from the gods even. The Nexus Scion began her teleportaion spell. In a blink of an eye, he was gone, forgetting he had left his teleportation sphere upon him. At the same time, the entire zone boar witness that &quot;Dr****** has run like a cowardly dog!&quot; And the masses rejoiced.<br>
<br>
He was cool enough to OOC and congratulate me and I was quick to acknowledge the Scion did me a favor lol. He told me he would like his revenge someday, and he has yet to come claim it. I know I owe him that match, and here's hoping I can finish my quest for Endless Quiver and AM3 before that happens. Oh yeah, if by chance that certain SK should read this, Cheguevara Castro still lives. He just goes by another name.<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :hat --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/pimp.gif ALT=":hat"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=599712" target="top"><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center">Jadin Greenstarr</div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center">Veteran Outrider of Tunare</div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://pub107.ezboard.com/bedgeofvalor" target="top"><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Edge of Valor</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center">Officer of Alliances</div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=caemus>Caemus</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 72<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(8/28/03 2:53 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3944.topic&index=15>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   